<br>
In preparation for another glorious Mage centered event, I’d like to begin gathering names of Mages with Epics that would like to gather to take on some big game targets in non-conventional ways.<br>
<br>
(You don’t HAVE to have your Epic, I’d welcome any Mages that want to tag along, but I’d like to focus on an army of Epic pets flattening some fun stuff.)<br>
<br>
It would be <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>GLORIOUS</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> if we had 30+ Epic/61+ Mages gathered to take down something monumentous.<br>
<br>
I'll be logging a list of interested Mages here: (The target isn't 100% certain yet, so let's discuss it!)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Cometus Aurelius - 52 Mage - Epic<br>
Zacatac Soulwanderer - 62 Mage - Epic<br>
Xita - 53 Mage (Get to G-Vocarate level)<br>
Adydar Worldwalker - 62 Mage<br>
Melvyn Ghostwalker - 62 Mage<br>
Kalahad Thundersoul - 65 Mage<br>
Lofwyr - 63 Epic<br>
Malkar Zauviir - 57 Mage - Epic<br>
Melik D`Moraine - 58 Mage<br>
Shelbydog Onocop - 65 Mage - Epic<br>
Niban - 57 Mage - Epic<br>
Helf PetCommander - 64 Mage<br>
Derrial - 55 Mage<br>
</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
I’ve been wracking my brain for a while thinking of some viable targets to take out and here are a few that come to mind:<br>
<br>
Velketor the Sorceror: (Perhaps a lucky Mage will walk away with some new Booties.)<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=5510">eqbeastiary.allakhazam.co...ml?id=5510</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
Trakanon: (Mana robe among other goodies.)<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=4503">eqbeastiary.allakhazam.co...ml?id=4503</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
Dragon Necropolis: (Depends on how many Mages we have, but there are some big targets here.)<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?zone=121">eqbeastiary.allakhazam.co...l?zone=121</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
Nathyn Illuminious: (Drops a spiffy Charisma Robe, but he’s a 1,000,000 hp mob.. would be a fun fight.)<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=8070">eqbeastiary.allakhazam.co...ml?id=8070</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
Perhaps a stroll through Akheva or Umbral Planes?<br>
<br>
I had thought about Western Waste dragons, but faction might be an issue for some.<br>
<br>
Perhaps the newly revamped Skyshrine? (Again, faction might be a concern.)<br>
<br>
I would suggest some PoP encounters, but they are either limited by numbers or flags.<br>
<br>
Who’s up for some Mayhem and where would you like to hit my Mage friends???<br>
<br>
There's no current set time or place for a raid, just post if you'd be interested.<br>
<br>
Goji<br>
